infographic relation-dagre-flow-tb-compact-card
data
  title Open RAN Agent at a glance
  desc Operator surface, BEAM control ownership, native boundary, and evidence loop.
  nodes
    - id ops
      label Operator surface
      desc Dashboard, skills, local CI
    - id ranctl
      label bin/ranctl
      desc Single mutable action entrypoint
    - id core
      label ran_core and ran_config
      desc Policy, topology, observability
    - id du
      label DU path
      desc ran_du_high plus scheduler host
    - id fapi
      label ran_fapi_core
      desc Canonical IR and capability checks
    - id native
      label Native boundary
      desc fapi_rt_gateway and adapters
    - id runtime
      label Backend runtime
      desc DU low, fronthaul, vendor workers
    - id evidence
      label Artifacts and evidence
      desc Plans, captures, remote runs
  relations
    ops -> ranctl
    ranctl -> core
    ranctl -> du
    du -> fapi
    fapi -> native
    native -> runtime
    ranctl -> evidence
    core -> evidence
theme
  palette #0f766e #1d4ed8 #0f172a #ea580c #475569
  base
    text
      font-family Inter, ui-sans-serif, system-ui
